entries.title: Curiosity and learning
entries.entry: Today I learnt a lot about a topic I was curious about. I'm so glad I took the time to research and learn more about it. I'm excited to apply what I learnt in my studies and projects. I'm also looking forward to learning more about this topic in the future.

entries.title: Self-care routines
entries.entry: I've been trying to make sure I take care of myself better. I've been trying to make sure I get enough sleep, eat healthy, and take breaks when I need to. It's been hard to stick to my routines but I'm trying my best to make sure I'm taking care of myself.

entries.title: Gratitude challenge
entries.entry: Today I tried a gratitude challenge. I wrote down three things I was grateful for and it really made me appreciate the little things in life. I'm thankful for my family, friends, and the opportunities I have been given.

entries.title: Compliment challenge
